  <brief_title>Pharmacokinetics of Tranexamic Acid (TXA) in Children Undergoing Repair of Congenital Heart Defects Utilizing Cardiopulmonary Bypass</brief_title>
  <official_title>Pharmacokinetics of Tranexamic Acid (TXA) in Children Undergoing Repair of Congenital Heart Defects Utilizing Cardiopulmonary Bypass</official_title>
