  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to measure blood levels of TXA in children having cardiac
      surgery which requires cardiopulmonary bypass. TXA is used to reduce bleeding during surgery.
      This study will help determine if the current dosing of TXA results in therapeutic blood
      levels.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
